  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd, \u0b8a\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b95\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bcb\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb8\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "We strongly condemn the attack on protesters, journalists - Lawyer Sukhas",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Tamil National People's Front's media speaker and lawyer K. Chukas has said that we strongly condemn the friendly attack on the protest groups and journalists who fought in the democratic way.",
        "We strongly condemn the brutal attack by the government machinery on the protesting groups who fought in the democratic way and on the journalists present there.",
        "Although the aspirations of the Tamil people are not reflected in this struggle, it is contrary to the political culture of the Tamil nation that we who are working for the liberation of the Tamil nation are blindly watching the dictatorship and anarchy being carried out there as a struggle to ensure the interests of the fraternal Sinhalese nation.",
        "The attack is a harbinger of how the newly-appointed government will fare in the future.",
        "Attempting to suppress democratic struggles by force is the height of anarchy. Attempting to suppress the media, which is described as the fourth pillar of democracy, which operates with the tip of a pen, should be seen as the height of cowardice and stupidity.",
        "Our voices will always be raised against any threats to democratic values. We express our support to the #people and media relations affected by the attacks of the state machinery and the army."
      ],
